author: Associated Press
title: Man who killed Denver transit officer was 'radical Muslim' | Daily Mail Online
text: Former US serviceman who shot and killed a Denver transit officer was a 'radical Muslim who had jihadist material in his backpack' and had recently been kicked out of a mosque Joshua Cummings, 37, allegedly shot dead Scott Von Lanken, 56, in Denver late Tuesday night Cummings, who is from Texas, was reported to have had jihadist material in his backpack at the time of his arrest He is also said to have been kicked out of a mosque in Texas The shooting happened late Tuesday night near Union Station, a hub for buses and trains, and the city's pedestrian mall Published: 01:59 GMT, 2 February 2017 | Updated: 04:04 GMT, 2 February 2017 55 shares
